snippet.title: Touhou DollDraft Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1341460/Touhou_DollDraft/

Touhou DollDraft is a game in which you form teams comprising “dollified” Touhou Project characters and send them into battle against each other.
